Announcement has been made of the engagement of Dr. Kristen A. Zarfos of Guilford, Conn., to William A. Whalen 3d of Windham Center, Conn. The wedding is planned for May. The prospective bride, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Theodore Zarfos of Smithsburg, Md., is a staff emergency physician with the Middlesex Memorial Hospital in Middletown, Conn., and the Shoreline Clinic in Essex, Conn. Mr. Whalen, son of Dr. and Mrs. Whalen Jr., is completing doctoral work in genetics at the University of Connecticut.